Title: KitchenAid® Feed Tube Pusher
Description: Ensures that every bit of food reaches the slicing/shredding disc. Works with both 9 & 11-cup food processors.

Title: KitchenAid® 12-Cup Food Processor with 2 Bowls
Description: An ideal model for the creative cook, this food processor features a generous 12-cup work bowl and a powerful induction motor that produces consistent results. Versatile discs handle a variety of tasks, from slicing to kneading dough.

Title: KitchenAid® Silicone Tipped Tongs
Description: High quality stainless steel and heat resistant tips up to 500 degrees make the Silicone Tipped Tongs a must-have kitchen tool. And scratching your non-stick surface is a thing of the past, because the silicone tips will just glide right along it. The tongs are dishwasher safe and feature a locking mechanism for compact, convenient storage.

Title: KitchenAid® Box Grater
Description: Easily grate, slice and store using this KitchenAid Box Grater with Covered Container. The grater is made of strong stainless steel and dishwasher safe. Use the 3-cup container to store your freshly grated goods. The container is dishwasher, freezer and microwave safe.

Title: KitchenAid® Multi-Slicer
Description: This dishwasher safe, Multi-Slicer with non-slip handles is sure to become a favorite tool for you in the kitchen. Included is an apple slicer, which also removes the core, a julienne slicer for smaller strips of vegetables and a French fry slicer for larger pieces. Keep all of the pieces together and protected in the convenient storage container.

Title: KitchenAid® Cup Grater
Description: Grate and store your favorite hard cheese or chocolate with the KitchenAid® Cup Grater. Fine and course sharp stainless steel blades are included. The soft, non-slip clear container with lid is perfect to store your freshly grated goods. Clean up is easy, as everything is dishwasher safe.

Title: KitchenAid® All Metal Grain Mill
Description: This all-metal attachment grinds wheat, oats, corn, rice, and other low-moisture, low-oil grains. Using freshly milled grains brings a hearty taste and texture to your baked goods. When you bake with home ground flour you will get all of the good you could possible get from a grain. Choose from 'cracked' to extra-fine consistency. Includes a cleaning brush.

Title: KitchenAid® Stand Mixer Attachment Pack
Description: KitchenAid® Stand Mixer Attachment Pack with Food Grinder, Rotor Slicer/Shredder and Sausage Stuffer Kit attachments.

Title: KitchenAid® 7 Speed Hand Mixer
Description: This stylish hand mixer features a 7-speed electronic digital control that includes two slow stir speeds and one high whip speed. Soft start® electronic control adjusts to the resistance of what you're mixing for smooth, consistent operation.
